```plantuml
@startuml YashwantChauhan_SDL

actor User
participant "Web Browser" as Browser
participant "Django Views" as Views
participant "Django Models" as Models
participant "ML Classifier" as ML
participant "Database" as DB

User -> Browser: Accesses Web Interface
Browser -> Views: GET / (Home Page)
Views -> Browser: Render Home Template

User -> Browser: Submits Login Form
Browser -> Views: POST /login (Credentials)
Views -> Models: authenticate_user()
Models -> DB: Query User Table
DB --> Models: User Data
Models --> Views: Authentication Result
Views -> Browser: Redirect to Dashboard (Success) or Error (Failure)

User -> Browser: Uploads Traffic File
Browser -> Views: POST /upload (File Data)
Views -> ML: preprocess_and_classify()
ML --> Views: Attack Classification Results
Views -> Models: save_detection_history()
Models -> DB: Insert History Record
DB --> Models: Confirmation
Views -> Browser: Render Results Page with Recommendations

User -> Browser: Views History
Browser -> Views: GET /history
Views -> Models: get_user_history()
Models -> DB: Query History Table
DB --> Models: History Records
Models --> Views: Formatted History
Views -> Browser: Render History Page

@enduml
```